  <p>Accounting is one of those things where a few dollars spent on software can quickly be recouped at tax time.  Plus there are other non-tax time savers in invoicing, payments, etc&#8212;especially important as you get into contract or full-time employees.</p>


	<p>I&#8217;ve gone with Quickbooks in the past and was very happy with the decision. More than a few clients or more than one employee (you), I&#8217;d head in that direction.</p>
