  <p>I have been using quickbooks for a while now and it serves its purpose. My accountant uses it and it makes it easy if I have problems. He knows how it works and   makes for easy answers to my accounting questions. I have never used some of the other web based products but i&#8217;m thinking, if you are forseeing the need for help from an accountant than you may want to look at a tool they are familiar with.
My two cents&#8230;</p>


	<p>Cheers</p>


